@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oizeij(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.58) + (tmp + 0.47 / v2 + 0.19)) * v2)
    v2 = wp.abs(v2)
    tmp = ((v2 - (v1 + 0.05 * tmp + 0.57)) + v0)
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.54) - 0.06) * (wp.exp(v1 + 0.68) * 0.66))
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.96)) * (wp.cos(v0 + 0.99) - 0.00))
    data[tid] = v0
